 the link to download the application form format.Download Registration Form in PDFList of Documents RequiredFollowing documents would be required at the time of Bhavantar Bhugtan Yojana registrationLand registration document and loan passbook.In case of Sikmi/Patta land, letter of authorization and loan passbook of original land owner.Aadhar number or receipt of Aadhar registration.Copy of first page of bank passbook where account number and name is mentioned. The bank account should be with any nationalized bank or the co-operative central bank branch.Mukhyamantri Bhavantar Bhugtan Yojana PortalBhavantar Bhugtan Yojana Registration Portal is http://mpeuparjan.nic.inHELPLINE For any help regarding the registration, the interested applicants can contact at euparjanmp@gmail.com o visit the official website at http://mpeuparjan.nic.inIMAGE SOURCE AND CREDITS: mpeuparjan.nic.in and mpinfo.org  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}